# ğŸ“„ DocuMind (AI Document Intelligence)

**Architected by Smit Godiyal**

An AI-powered document analysis engine that allows users to "chat" with their PDF files. It uses **Retrieval Augmented Generation (RAG)** to ingest complex documents (contracts, research papers, financial reports) and allows users to query them using natural language.

